# gitbook-plugin-tbfed-pagefooter

* 插件配置

```javascript
"tbfed-pagefooter": {
  "copyright":"&copy Taobao FED Team",
  "modify_label": "该文件修订时间：",
  "modify_format": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss"
}
```

> copyright 和 modify_label 支持 html 代码
=======
# gitbook-plugin-tbfed-pagefooter

* 插件配置

```javascript
"tbfed-pagefooter": {
  "copyright":"&copy Taobao FED Team",
  "modify_label": "该文件修订时间：",
  "modify_format": "YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss"
}
```

> copyright 和 modify_label 支持 html 代码
